            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">Yan Yuan was attending to the master, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">and the master said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">“Hui, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">if someone is wise all by himself </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">this is what people dislike, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">if someone is noble by himself, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en">this is what people dislike, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en">if someone is rich all by himself, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en">this is what people dislike. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en">If one is noble </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en">but able to concede, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en">then people like his being noble; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en">if one is rich </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en">but [...] [then people like his being rich]” </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">Yan Yuan was attending to the master, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">and the master said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">“Hui, the master achieves ritual propriety </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en">by relying on humanity.” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en">Yan Yuan stood up </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en">and answered: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en">“As I am not bright, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en">I am unable to dwell there even for a short while.” (=I don’t get it) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en">The master said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en">“Sit, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en">I will tell you.” </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en">When you talk about something </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en">and it is not right, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en">your mouth should not mention it; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en">when you watch something </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en">and it is not right, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en">your eyes should not watch it; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en">if you listen to something </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en">and it is not right, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en">your ears should not listen to it; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en">if you move (somewhere) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.11" xml:lang="en">and it is not right, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-3a.12" xml:lang="en">your body should not move there.” </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en">Yan Yuan retreated </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en">and for many days did not come out. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en">[...] [asked] him saying: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en">“Why are you so troubled?” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en">He said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en">“It is like this: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en">I have recently heard a talk from the master, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.8" xml:lang="en">I want to enact it and I am not able to do it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.9" xml:lang="en">I want to forget about it and I am not able to do it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-4a.10" xml:lang="en">therefore I am troubled.” </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en">The xx Zi Yu asked Zi Gong: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en">“Who is worthier, Confucius or Wu Zi Chang?” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en">Zi Gong answered: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en">“If the master rules a city with ten households, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en">he is happy, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en">if he rules a country with ten thousand households, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.7" xml:lang="en">he is also happy, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-5a.8" xml:lang="en">being so then [he is worthier than Zi Chang.]” </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en">“Who is worthier, Confucius or Yu?” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en">Zi Gong answered: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en">“Yu regulated the rivers all under Heaven, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en">[...] hereby establishing his name. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en">Confucius regulated the Odes and the Documents </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en">and also established his name, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en">being so then he is worthier than Yu.” </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en">“Who is worthier, Confucius or Shun?” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en">Zi Gong answered: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en">“Shun ruled all under Heaven </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en">[the master being so is worthier than Shun]. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en">In general the eyes should not wander, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en">just seek what is one has decided to see, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en">should not covet </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.4" xml:lang="en">nor escape, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.5" xml:lang="en">and as for the quick and slow (rhythm) of a sound (=music), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.6" xml:lang="en">it should be in accord to the abundance or scarcity (of the public). </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.7" xml:lang="en">[...] beautiful neck. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.8" xml:lang="en">The shoulders should not be (too much) down </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.9" xml:lang="en">nor up, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.10" xml:lang="en">the body should not be bent </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0054_tls_001-9a.11" xml:lang="en">nor lax. </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
